TopicTitle: What to do while waiting for rescue

Articles.Content:
I wanted to show you guys my very first fanart I'm posting! (this is a really old image, been meaning to post this for a while now actually)

Jeb accidentally fainted from excitement while trying to land on the Mun, faceplanting right into the Staging button...
Jumping, then running and sliding. Always fun. At least in low grav.
